      <item>
        <title>Setup, Reset And Drop Database</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;TAGS:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;ruby  rails  migration  database  setup  reset  drop 
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Setup, Reset and Drop Database Via Rails Console.&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Setting up the database using &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;rake db:setup&lt;/code&gt; will create the database and migrate the migration files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rake&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:setup&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, Resetting the database using&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rake&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:reset&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;will re-migrate the migration files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But, Drop the database using&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rake&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:drop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;will delete the the database itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;rake db:reset&lt;/code&gt; equals &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;rake db:drop db:setup&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe width=&quot;100%&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/eQirPQNBy9Q&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
</description>
