      <item>
        <title>Joining Two Tables Via Rails Migration</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;TAGS:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;ruby  rails  migration  database  join 
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Joining Two Tables Via Rails Migration.&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;First, We suppose that you have two tables at least.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In our example, we have &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;books&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;authors&lt;/code&gt; tables, so we can join them using migration by adding &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;references&lt;/code&gt; column which is author’s &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;id&lt;/code&gt; of the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;book&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Or in other word, each record in &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;books&lt;/code&gt; has its author’s &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;id&lt;/code&gt; as:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rails&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;g&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;migration&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;AddAuthorRefToBooks&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;author&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:references&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will generate a migration file to add this column as:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;AddAuthorRefToBooks&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;ActiveRecord&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Migration&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;change&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;add_reference&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:books&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:author&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;index: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;foreign_key: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then, Apply changes to database using:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rake&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:migrate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that you can undo this migration using:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rake&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:rollback&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now, You need to manually join these table via &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;model&lt;/code&gt; by :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;Adding &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;has_many :books&lt;/code&gt; in the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;author&lt;/code&gt; model&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;Adding &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;belongs_to :author&lt;/code&gt; in the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;book&lt;/code&gt; model&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/blockquote&gt;

